## Default payment method

> Sample Request

```json
{
  "unbillKey": "<%= config.auth %>",
  "paymentMethodId": "566595c8ce88ccec69328566"
}
```

> Sample Response

```json
{
  "_id": "580e3754dec21e861b5a3718",
  "type": "card",
  "card": {
    "number": "XXXX4242",
    "brand": "visa",
    "type": "credit",
    "expDate": "2016-12-01T12:00:00.000Z"
  },
  "status": "verified",
  "default": true
}
```

Set a payment method as the `default` for bill payments.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/payment/set-default`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`paymentMethodId` | Payment method ID.

### Returns

Returns an updated payment object.